hopobject.body: Could I make an appointment to see ? futzuki reflexology massage mat Debbie and Ruzwana agree that you can make the most out of being in the minority, but it's not easy. "You are more unique, but you have to fight certain assumptions," Ruzwana says. Debbie feels less alone than she used to, as she's made an effort to seek out and form close bonds with other UK-based female entrepreneurs. "It's a funny life to choose [and] it can distance you from your peers," she says.
